history.content: Chemistry is looking for a reader for a CHEM 195/295 course on Machine Learning. The position is an average of 10 hr/week grading homework assignments. No Chemistry knowledge required, but working knowledge in Machine Learning is highly desired. Qualified candidates may be Undergraduates with Junior or Senior Status, or Graduate students in good standing, with a minimum GPA of 3.0. Please contact teachchemistry@berkeley.edu with your resume and a brief statement on your machine learning background.
history.subject: Reader in Machine Learning Sought by Chem Department
